Git Hooks
================================================================================
This folder can be used to automatically add functionality whenever you perform
an action in the git repository.

For a while I had Tim Pope's ctags hook installed, but I decided to remove it
because ctags tend to cause more errors in vim than I am happy with.
See here for the setup:
http://tbaggery.com/2011/08/08/effortless-ctags-with-git.html
